Package: mcpr
Title: Model Context Protocol for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aleksander", "Dietrichson", , "dietrichson@chi2labs.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Expose R functions, files, or entire packages through the Model
    Context Protocol (MCP). This package provides a simple, decorator-based
    system for creating MCP servers that integrate with AI assistants like
    Claude Desktop. Following patterns established by plumber, mcpr makes
    it easy to connect R code with large language models.
